{
  "metadata": {
    "synopsis": "Avatar shadowheart reflects on the events of the shar temple and the death of Nightsong. Along with what that means for the future. Avatar can choose to change their hairstyle.",
    "how_to_trigger": "1. Kill Nightsong with Shadowheart2. Long rest"
  },
  "dialogue": {
    "21": {
      "id": "21",
      "speaker": "Narrator",
      "text": "*Fatigue creeps through your limbs, and presses on your mind. Yet it is a pleasurable sort of weariness - one founded in accomplishment.*",
      "context": "",
      "checkflags": [],
      "setflags": [],
      "ruletags": [],
      "approval": [],
      "rolls": "",
      "goto": "",
      "link": "17",
      "is_end": false,
      "node_type": "normal",
      "children": {
        "24": {
          "id": "24",
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "text": "*You slew the Nightsong. You caused the Sel\u00fbnite enclave at Last Light to fall. All for the Dark Lady. Now you are her Chosen.*",
          "context": "",
          "checkflags": [
            "ORI_Shadowheart_State_DestroyedHaven"
          ],
          "setflags": [],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "17",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {}
        },
        "23": {
          "id": "23",
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "text": "*You slew the daughter of Sel\u00fbne for the Dark Lady. Now you are her Chosen.*",
          "context": "",
          "checkflags": [],
          "setflags": [],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "20",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "17": {
              "id": "17",
              "speaker": "Narrator",
              "text": "*Your glory, bought with the blood of others. It was worth it, was it not...?*",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "20",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "15": {
                  "id": "15",
                  "speaker": "Shadowheart",
                  "text": "Of course it was worth it. Your whole life has been leading to this.",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "20",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "7": {
                      "id": "7",
                      "speaker": "Narrator",
                      "text": "*Lady Shar's favour is worth everything. You would have gladly done what she asked a thousand times over.*",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "20",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {}
                    }
                  }
                },
                "0": {
                  "id": "0",
                  "speaker": "Shadowheart",
                  "text": "Banish such doubts - they only distract from your faith.",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "20",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "3": {
                      "id": "3",
                      "speaker": "Narrator",
                      "text": "*Yet what of your lover? Would Lady Shar approve of that distraction? Perhaps you can earn the right to share your heart, if you excel in all other areas of service.*",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [
                        "ORI_State_Partnered"
                      ],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "20",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {}
                    },
                    "9": {
                      "id": "9",
                      "speaker": "Narrator",
                      "text": "*Your dedication has already brought you far already. Who is to say what greatness awaits?*",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "20",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {}
                    }
                  }
                },
                "4": {
                  "id": "4",
                  "speaker": "Shadowheart",
                  "text": "You cannot lie. Part of you regrets the cost in life. Yet it was Lady Shar's will.",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "11",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "1": {
                      "id": "1",
                      "speaker": "Narrator",
                      "text": "*A small sacrifice, compared to the infinite glories that await.*",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "11",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "20": {
                          "id": "20",
                          "speaker": "Narrator",
                          "text": "*You are destined to be at Lady Shar's right hand, while others lose her favour.*",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "11",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {
                            "10": {
                              "id": "10",
                              "speaker": "Narrator",
                              "text": "*Like your Mother Superior. She marked the wound on your hand. She sent you on a mission that nearly cost you everything.*",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "11",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "2": {
                                  "id": "2",
                                  "speaker": "Shadowheart",
                                  "text": "She must be purged. The Dark Lady demands it.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "11",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {
                                    "11": {
                                      "id": "11",
                                      "speaker": "Narrator",
                                      "text": "*She will become a footnote, once you take her place. Your glory will be unparalleled.*",
                                      "context": "",
                                      "checkflags": [],
                                      "setflags": [],
                                      "ruletags": [],
                                      "approval": [],
                                      "rolls": "",
                                      "goto": "",
                                      "link": "",
                                      "is_end": false,
                                      "node_type": "normal",
                                      "children": {
                                        "22": {
                                          "id": "22",
                                          "speaker": "Narrator",
                                          "text": "*Yet you still feel like a novice, at times. To be the Chosen of Shar demands certain... gravitas.*",
                                          "context": "",
                                          "checkflags": [],
                                          "setflags": [],
                                          "ruletags": [],
                                          "approval": [],
                                          "rolls": "",
                                          "goto": "",
                                          "link": "",
                                          "is_end": false,
                                          "node_type": "normal",
                                          "children": {
                                            "12": {
                                              "id": "12",
                                              "speaker": "Shadowheart",
                                              "text": "You still wear your hair like a trainee. Time for something more... commanding.",
                                              "context": "",
                                              "checkflags": [],
                                              "setflags": [
                                                "Shadowheart_InParty_State_PreparingHairChange"
                                              ],
                                              "ruletags": [],
                                              "approval": [],
                                              "rolls": "",
                                              "goto": "",
                                              "link": "",
                                              "is_end": false,
                                              "node_type": "normal",
                                              "children": {
                                                "13": {
                                                  "id": "13",
                                                  "speaker": "",
                                                  "text": "",
                                                  "context": "",
                                                  "checkflags": [],
                                                  "setflags": [],
                                                  "ruletags": [],
                                                  "approval": [],
                                                  "rolls": "",
                                                  "goto": "",
                                                  "link": "",
                                                  "is_end": false,
                                                  "node_type": "visualstate",
                                                  "children": {
                                                    "18": {
                                                      "id": "18",
                                                      "speaker": "Narrator",
                                                      "text": "*So be it. There will be no rest for you yet, but come dawn, you will even closer to Lady Shar, in image and spirit.*",
                                                      "context": "CinematicNodeContext: Shadowheart sits up.",
                                                      "checkflags": [],
                                                      "setflags": [],
                                                      "ruletags": [],
                                                      "approval": [],
                                                      "rolls": "",
                                                      "goto": "",
                                                      "link": "",
                                                      "is_end": true,
                                                      "node_type": "normal",
                                                      "children": {}
                                                    }
                                                  }
                                                }
                                              }
                                            },
                                            "16": {
                                              "id": "16",
                                              "speaker": "Shadowheart",
                                              "text": "That will come in time - your actions will speak for themselves. Now, rest.",
                                              "context": "",
                                              "checkflags": [],
                                              "setflags": [],
                                              "ruletags": [],
                                              "approval": [],
                                              "rolls": "",
                                              "goto": "",
                                              "link": "",
                                              "is_end": false,
                                              "node_type": "normal",
                                              "children": {
                                                "14": {
                                                  "id": "14",
                                                  "speaker": "Narrator",
                                                  "text": "*The oblivion of sleep awaits. You hasten towards it.*",
                                                  "context": "CinematicNodeContext: Shadowheart closes her eyes,",
                                                  "checkflags": [],
                                                  "setflags": [],
                                                  "ruletags": [],
                                                  "approval": [],
                                                  "rolls": "",
                                                  "goto": "",
                                                  "link": "",
                                                  "is_end": true,
                                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                                  "children": {}
                                                }
                                              }
                                            }
                                          }
                                        }
                                      }
                                    }
                                  }
                                },
                                "8": {
                                  "id": "8",
                                  "speaker": "Shadowheart",
                                  "text": "The Mother Superior always hindered your ambitions. Yet now you will unseat her. Ironic.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "11",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {}
                                },
                                "5": {
                                  "id": "5",
                                  "speaker": "Shadowheart",
                                  "text": "She saved your life, and made you who you are today. You owe her much.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "22",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {
                                    "19": {
                                      "id": "19",
                                      "speaker": "Narrator",
                                      "text": "*No matter. Anything owed belongs to the Nightsinger, ultimately. The loss of your mentor will herald your own triumph.*",
                                      "context": "",
                                      "checkflags": [],
                                      "setflags": [],
                                      "ruletags": [],
                                      "approval": [],
                                      "rolls": "",
                                      "goto": "",
                                      "link": "22",
                                      "is_end": false,
                                      "node_type": "normal",
                                      "children": {}
                                    }
                                  }
                                }
                              }
                            }
                          }
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}